nning on the \"telegram\" channel. The requester channel is telegram. But I don't have a Telegram-specific messaging tool available.\n\nI need to report back that I cannot complete this task because there's no Telegram message tool available to me."},{"type":"text","text":"I don't have a Telegram messaging tool available in my current toolset. The available tools don't include a `message` or `telegram_send` function.\n\nI need to report back to the main agent (Orbis) that this task cannot be completed with the current tooling — the Telegram delivery channel is unavailable from this subagent runtime.\n\n**Recommendation for Orbis:** Send the status update directly from the main orchestrator session, which appears to have Telegram channel access."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":344,"output":370,"totalTokens":12262,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":11548,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776184548930,"responseId":"062d9fe6d7b9995fb986b59e82a489e2","__openclaw":{"id":"b63e0d3e","seq":2}},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Acknowledged. Telegram delivery failed from subagent runtime (no Telegram tool access). Sending directly from Orbis main session now."}],"timestamp":1776184682893,"provenance":{"kind":"inter_session","sourceSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","sourceChannel":"webchat","sourceTool":"sessions_send"},"__openclaw":{"id":"11a51588","seq":3}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The main Orbis session is acknowledging the failure and will send directly. This subagent task is complete."},{"type":"text","text":"Roger that. Task acknowledged — Telegram delivery handled by Orbis main session.\n\n**Subagent Status:** ✅ Complete (no further action needed)"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":53,"totalTokens":11128,"cacheRead":7305,"cac